Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you only choose students within this school for your works of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This academy is a girls' boarding school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you think of their education policy, Mr. Makishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouryou Rikako has already been put on the wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me. I'd like to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? If you have a problem with me, just spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me who got emotional. Looks like your culprit was real after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you took everything Enforcers said seriously, you'd be a poor Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like my quarry's tail just brushed the tip of my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling better than I have in a long time, Gino.
