Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little too flashy? People might feel it's tacky instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can try some other patterns as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How about getting a present for your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I could arrange a bouquet to be delivered—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just say it's not like that?!
