Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The use of cyborg technology for medical purposes is now commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's still rare to see someone like Chairman Senguji who,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,except for his brain and nervous system, is entirely cybernetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery to me why other people haven't given up those limiting bodies of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Limiting, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Plato said that our souls were imprisoned in our bodies.{they sure do like their literary namedrops, huh}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a bad mood already, Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tried to smoke, that thing tried to bite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about? Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, please don't worry about it. I'm curious too, so I don't mind.{you wot m8}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finding new pleasures in my life all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that overcoming aging would lead to such happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the kind of thing you can't understand until you have a cybernetic body yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But even with the latest technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's estimated that the brain's lifespan is about 150 years at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that we're still quite a ways away from complete cyberization of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take my brain to its limits, I can squeeze a bit more life out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm counting on them to find a breakthrough in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If that actually happens, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of immortality will have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that God created man in his own image.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time for us humans to become a little more like God?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:06:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about gaining eternal youth and immortality by becoming a cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Life as a latent criminal isn't the sort of thing you'd want to go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... As society progresses, the rights of latent criminals may improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder your Psycho-Pass always manages to stay so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,According to a survey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems that a majority of people have answered that they feel reluctant to be more than 50% cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand the reluctance that those people feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it's a matter of degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, take yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the cyborg too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't use artificial arms, legs, or organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You do, however, carry some form of portable information terminal, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes... but doesn't everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A costume device, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And at home, you probably have home automation and an AI secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen to you if all the data in those devices was lost due to some kind of disaster or accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to do any work until it was restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you entrust so much of your everyday life to those electronic devices,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the argument that you're not a cyborg isn't very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To you, those portable terminals are already your second brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be said that the history of science is a history of the expansion of the human body's functionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the history of man's cyberization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's a matter of degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.54,get out,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.1\c&H4AA4D3&\alpha&H30&\b1\frx0\fry356\org(680,-100)\fscx181\fscy158\pos(654,425)}P{\c&H439CCB&}r{\c&H57A0C6&}i{\c&H1B3881&}v{\c&H0C2C7D&}a{\c&H141E61&}t{\c&H080F40&}e {\c&H020D3A&}Prop{\c&H0D134C&}e{\c&H05173C&}r{\c&H000429&}t{\c&H02072E&}y\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H16629D&}N{\c&H1B6DAC&}o {\c&H4E97D0&}T{\c&H2592D1&}r{\c&H021C51&}e{\c&H011136&}sp{\c&H00113D&}a{\c&H001667&}s{\c&H05106D&}s{\c&H050E63&}i{\c&H02074D&}n{\c&H030A4C&}g
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.46,get out,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&H002358&\pos(1010,380)\fscx40\fscy35\alpha&H15&}Private Property\N\N\N\NNo Trespassing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's me, Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see much environment Holo in use here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Professor Saiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me "professor". How many years do you think it's been since I quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsunemori Akane, an Inspector at the Public Safety Bureau. Thanks for seeing me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, and welcome to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.67,lt,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.6\blur1.2\alpha&H30&\c&H948579&\fscx42\fscy35\frz328.9\pos(706.571,126.001)}Clinical Psychology {\c&H8B7C70&}Special {\c&H7C6F65&}Lecture A\N {\c&H948579&}Sibyl Education Investig{\c&H8E7F73&}ation {\c&H7B6E64&}Research {\c&H71655C&}Center
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is coffee okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as well, since coffee's all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tsunemori Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from Chiba prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your athletic ability isn't bad, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why you can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of your parents are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're worried about their only daughter not finding a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They were opposed to you working at the Bureau, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And, your grandfather or grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She treated you with great affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you're quite the grandma's girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's often true that the more time you spend with the elderly during your childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the better you can get along with Holo Avatar AIs during your adult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fit that pattern, Ms. Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as sharp as ever, Saiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How... did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,People manifest all sorts of signs unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get the knack of it, you can read those signs pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiga Jouji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You specialize in clinical psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As I worked as a psychiatric examiner and assisted in investigations and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,my main focus shifted to criminal research before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two favors to ask you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'd like you to give this Inspector an intensive short course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to learn about profiling and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's an outdated method, but I'm very interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I became interested recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hermit. I actually feel grateful for the opportunity to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the list of past course attendees that you keep with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a request from the Bureau?{order would make more sense, but he says request, so}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's a request from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was an order, I would've turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this guy must be the worst criminal to have lived since the creation of the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a high-level white-collar criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,who most likely keeps himself in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Possessing a unique charisma, he rarely kills people with his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, he chooses to influence the minds of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Much like a music conductor, he\N orchestrates one crime after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami, please explain what "charisma" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I used it to mean the nature of a hero or a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give that answer... twenty points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Charisma has three elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of a hero or a prophet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the ability to simply make you feel good when you're around them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the intelligence to eloquently talk about all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of those, which elements does this guy you're looking for have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he has all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shibata Yukimori, an art teacher at Ousou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's who he's supposed to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it turns out that he's actually an old man in a nursing home who has nothing to do with the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His background profile was altered and used by our suspect when he pretended to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite cruelly clever of him not to completely fake his background.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But he then chose to work as a teacher, placing himself right in the public eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he daring or just a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All the video data was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we were able to salvage was a short sound file.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two methods left: creating a traditional photofit picture or drawing a composite sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we tried both methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sound of it, they didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the only lead we have is the blurry picture Sasayama took, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you end up getting anything out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, it helped a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an incredible teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why his lectures aren't in the Bureau's archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'd put them in the archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This was around the time that both the Sibyl System and the university system existed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiga's special courses were set up for the Bureau's investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, a major concern came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The course attendees' Hues became cloudier and their Crime Coefficients rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A one-on-one lecture like the one you had today should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't see your Hue clouding that easily at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crazy that just listening to lectures could raise your Crime Coefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're at a dark swamp and you can't see the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to find out what's in that swamp, you have no choice but to jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiga's used to it since he's dived in so many times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like all his students can dive into that swamp and come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are gaps in their abilities, not to mention their basic suitability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like someone who'd dive right to the bottom... and yet come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, the Sibyl System decided that I couldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say is the most cunning animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One that's at no risk of extinction no matter how many are hunted and killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be humans.{the most dangerous game}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Too easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These days...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they no longer issue hunting licenses under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate what you've done for me, Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not ivory... is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I haven't shown this one to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excluding the mouthpiece, this pipe is made from Ouryou Rikako's bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm touching it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my mind regains its youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The souls of my terrified prey give me energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've overcome your body's aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that just leaves your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You maintain a healthy and sound life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,by sacrificing other lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if people only seek youth for their bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and lose sight of the means to cultivate their minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only natural that it would lead to an increase in the number of living dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy that comes from the thrill of the hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous reward that goes hand in hand with death, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In hunting, the tougher your prey is, the fresher the youth you can gain from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With all that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can arrange for your next prey to be most exquisite indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Enforcer from the Public Safety Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I guess checking Professor Saiga's lecture attendees list didn't help much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it goes sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Makishima is a living person,\N he's left a trace somewhere for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you brought Inspector Tsunemori to Saiga Jouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it because I asked him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you playing at? Are you trying to drag her into your problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,making her a latent criminal who strayed from the right path, like you?{snap}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you treating me like a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you {\i1}are{\i0} a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A brat who's confused about anything and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think we split the force into Inspectors and Enforcers in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to avoid the risk of having healthy people's Psycho-Passes get clouded by criminal investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We use latent criminals, who can never return to society, in our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely how you're able to fulfill your duty while keeping a healthy mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we here to solve crimes or protect our own Psycho-Passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you think matters more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to throw away your career?{sebastian pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to sacrifice everything you've built so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that I'm new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my senior, Inspector Ginoza, and I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But please don't forget that we're on equal footing in terms of our rank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm managing my Hue just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be my senior, but I'd appreciate it if you would refrain from questioning my ability
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at the workplace and in front of the Enforcers!{damn, girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to file a complaint with the bureau chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chance of you passing on that, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Ginoza's father is a latent criminal.{also, he is me}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a child when the Sibyl System had just been put into operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible misunderstandings and rumors about latent criminals were common in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If a family member happened to show a high Crime Coefficient,{until dake de}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that alone caused the rest of the family to be treated as if they were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he suffered quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When a detective gets deeply involved in an investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end the Sibyl System starts keeping an eye on them just like it does with the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said about committing crimes and cracking down on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're two sides of the same coin. The phenomenon called "crime".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Enforcers now, but before they created that position,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there were many detectives who ended up as latent criminals that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Ginoza's father was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he won't allow the other Inspectors to take risks on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, Kougami, his former colleague, suffered the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels as though he was betrayed twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First by his father and then by his colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he acts like that toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have family and friends of your own, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If your Psycho-Pass gets clouded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,those people will suffer the same hardships Nobuchika did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We Enforcers are here to prevent that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Kougami feels that way too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's oblivious to anything that's not related to that Makishima guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no interest in capturing him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What would even be the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you haven't noticed it yourself, so I'll tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami Shinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That name always seems to bring a smile to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:46.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,2200)\blur1}It seems all fairy tales {\alpha&HFF&}are dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.51,0:21:50.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:55.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:22:00.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:05.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Outside in the foggy haze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:11.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}a red moon glows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:16.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:22.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Do not avert your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:26.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Behind black bars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.43,0:22:29.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:31.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish there were a punishment for evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Always I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:37.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, grant us justice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}before chaos takes us all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:44.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Pay the price of fate and let us go together,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.76,0:22:49.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,500)\blur1}nameless beasts
